spec_data.Name: perl-Dist-Zilla-Plugin-CheckChangesHasContent
spec_data.Description:
This is a "before release" Dist::Zilla plugin that ensures that your
Changes file actually has some content since the last release. If it
doesn't find any, it will abort the release process.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:56:36 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Ensure Changes file has content before releasing
